# Basic-to-do-app
A basic To-Do List project for learning basic front-end development. (open source)

## Goal
Create a simple, clean to-do app to demonstrate HTML, CSS, and JavaScript fundamentals.

## Features
- Add tasks
- Mark tasks as completed
- Delete tasks
- Tasks saved in browser local storage

## Tech
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript (Vanilla)

## How to run locally
1. Download the files.
2. Open `index.html` in your browser.

